## finish work
When user says "finish work", run this in terminal:
1. Run: git add .
2. Ask Claude to summarize what files changed and write a commit message
3. Run: git commit -m "[auto-generated summary]"
4. Run: git push
Then confirm: "✅ Work saved and pushed to GitHub"

## pull
When user says "pull", run in terminal:
git pull
Then confirm: "✅ Latest code pulled"